Section 6.3 showed the necessary source code changes for applications to use usnet_sockets with
a build Ô¨Çag. For a project such as the HTTP library which directly imports the socket types it is
best to incorporate the import statement changes into the oÔ¨Écial source code tree. Maintaining a
